OL,4,Clonger considered chocolate
OL,6,FMcVitie's has changed the recipes of
OL,7,Fits Penguin and Club bars as
OL,8,Fmanufacturers re-evaluate their costs
OL,9,Fin line with soaring cocoa prices, as
OL,10,FWarren Nettleford reports.
OL,12,FTwo of Britain's most-loved chocolate
OL,13,Fbiscuits can no longer be described as
OL,14,Fchocolate, as they do not contain
OL,15,Fenough cocoa.
OL,17,FMcVitie's, the manufacturers behind
OL,18,FPenguin and Club bars, say they have
OL,19,Fchanged their recipes due to the
OL,20,Frising costs of cocoa.
