OL,6,FIt now means that the lunch box treats
OL,7,Fare being redefined as 'chocolate
OL,8,Fflavoured' as opposed to simply
OL,9,F'chocolate.'
OL,11,FThe soaring costs of cocoa has left
OL,12,Fmanufacturers trying to find cross-
OL,13,Fsaving solutions.
OL,15,FCocoa prices have more than doubled
OL,16,Fover the past two years due to poor
OL,17,Fweather and disease in West Africa,
OL,18,Fwhich supplies more than 70% of the
OL,19,Fworld's cocoa.
