OL,6,FIn a statement to the Guardian,
OL,7,FMcVitie's owner, Pladis said: "We made
OL,8,Fsome changes to McVitie's Penguin and
OL,9,FClub earlier this year, where we are
OL,10,Fusing a chocolate flavour coating with
OL,11,Fcocoa mass, rather than a chocolate
OL,12,Fcoating.
OL,14,FSpeaking to ITV News, chocolate maker
OL,15,FGiles Atwell said: "Cocoa prices went
OL,16,Fup to $12,000 (around #8,945) per
OL,17,Ftonne - nearly tripling in price.
