OL,6,F"That has left all major manufacturers
OL,7,Fscrambling to find cheaper ways of
OL,8,Fmaking chocolate; shrinking bars,
OL,9,Fshrinking chocolate to get around
OL,10,Fthat."
OL,12,F'Chocolate flavouring' indicates that
OL,13,Fthere are fewer quantities of cocoa in
OL,14,Fthe product, meaning it cannot be
OL,15,Flabelled as 'chocolate.'
