OL,6,FThe two treats now contain more palm
OL,7,Foil and shea oil than cocoa, as was
OL,8,Ffirst reported by the trade journal,
OL,9,FThe Grocer.
OL,11,FAnd with a change in ingredients comes
OL,12,Fa change in slogan.
OL,14,FThe Club bar's famous jingle, "If you
OL,15,Flike a lot of chocolate on your
OL,16,Fbiscuit, join our club..." has been
OL,17,Fchanged to "If you like a lot of
OL,18,Fbiscuit in your break, join our Club".
