OL,6,FOther sweet treat companies have been
OL,7,Fhit by the cocoa price hike, including
OL,8,FSwiss chocolatier Lindt, which
OL,9,Fincreased its price by 15.8% in the
OL,10,Ffirst half of 2025.
OL,12,FLindt said it was able to offset some
OL,13,Fof the higher cost of cocoa with long-
OL,14,Fterm contracts, but had to pass much
OL,15,Fof it on to consumers.
